        "func": "// msg.payload is the full JSON object coming from MQTT->json\nconst t = Number(msg.payload.temp_actual);\n\nif (Number.isNaN(t)) {\n    return null;   // drop bad values\n}\n\nmsg.payload = Math.round(t * 100) / 100;  // 2 decimals, stays a number\nreturn msg;\n",
